    <item>
      <title>巴西央行出手支撑全球最差货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/brazil-leads-global-losses-in-2024-as-fiscal-angst-takes-hold</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西资产今年年底的表现有望落后于所有主要货币，由于人们对总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦 (Luiz Inacio Lula da Silva) 解决不断膨胀的预算赤字的承诺日益怀疑，雷亚尔将遭遇 2020 年疫情冲击以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/brazil-leads-global-losses-in-2024-as-fiscal-angst-takes-hold</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 15:46:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京将百威英博俄罗斯子公司的控制权移交给当地公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/putin-hands-control-of-inbev-efes-s-russian-unit-to-local-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京已将百威英博合资企业的控制权交给了一家当地公司，此举打乱了百威英博通过与土耳其合作伙伴达成协议退出俄罗斯的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/putin-hands-control-of-inbev-efes-s-russian-unit-to-local-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 15:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
